{"tid":1561151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非】如果「拍卡再跳」都未做到，可以試下「拍卡前原地跳」","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:36:02.000Z","uid":114801,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fc8f563a349ce7fa6bcd4a38f32f48c9090ef0","tid":1561151,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n<br />\n「拍卡前原地跳」<br />\n<br />\n「拍卡再跳」<br />\n<br />\n「扮拍再跳」<br />\n<br />\n「直接跳」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試幻想你係藍屍，守住個閘口，見到個個出閘前都「跳」一下，你點知佢係有無拍卡？<br />\n等佢捉錯人又好；分散注意力掩護手足又好，係時候原地跳下，練下彈跳力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，強烈建議盡可能請罷搭"},{"pid":"ae99194fd644f71b1a478e5818dd58ab8e2149d5","tid":1561151,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3404e79b523b5f06dcd83918bfc297fd4a467720","tid":1561151,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"跳"},{"pid":"e2b81572f3735b9058a597b28c7b07993f4fc5fb","tid":1561151,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:21:02.000Z","msg":"跳"},{"pid":"0a8a4d98edc26de4d61c8d920878af7f846278b6","tid":1561151,"uid":80560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"r